    "description": "<p>You can maintain two separate trains of thought at once. You cannot be surprised or suffer Execution Attacks and one half of your mind can sleep while the other remains awake, though you must rest quietly to recover as normal. Once per round, as an Instant action when you fail a Mental save, you may accept one System Strain to reroll the save.</p>",
